Title: Videogaming
Presenters: Is Your MMO Teaching You About Life?
All Day Event: 'Massively Multiplayer Online games (MMOs) have been around for decades. Did you know they were teaching you things you could use in real-life?  We will examine the parallels and differences that many don't realize are there until they step back and look at them. Trying to get into a top guild? Better be ready to write a good application and have references and an interview. Sounds a lot like getting a job to me...'
